<plot>"Saturday Afternoon Theater" was a series than aired on Anaheim, California-based television station, KDOC, in the summer of 1991. Host Perry Cowen provided background information and trivia about movies. The first episode aired on May 25, 1991. The movie was "Wolf Call."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?478499</url></doc>
